 <P ALIGN="justify">Within the colorful tempo of New York City's Upper West Side, the Hotel Beacon welcomes visitors to this unique neighborhood.  With tree-lined streets and landmark buildings, you can experience The American Museum of Natural History, Lincoln Center, Central Park and the new Rose Center for Earth and Space.</P> <P ALIGN="justify">Amid this bustling enclave is a haven of comfort; a hotel with a different point of view.  Relaxed. Amiable. With handsomely decorated, oversized guestrooms and suites, each featuring a fully equipped kitchenette. Boasting wonderful views of Central Park, the Hudson River and the skyscrapers of midtown Manhattan.</P></TD></TR></TABLE></TD></TR></TABLE></TD>	</TR><TR><TD ALIGN="left"><TABLE BORDER=0 CELLSPACING="0" CELLPADDING="0" WIDTH="100%">	<TR>		<TD ROWSPAN="2" VALIGN="bottom"><IMG SRC="img/lobby_home.jpg" ALT="The Beacon Hotel" WIDTH="365" HEIGHT="267" HSPACE="15" VSPACE="15" BORDER="0"></TD><TD COLSPAN="2" ALIGN="center"><TABLE BORDER=0 CELLSPACING="0" CELLPADDING="0" WIDTH="90%">	<TR>		<TD ALIGN="left"><P ALIGN="justify">The Hotel Beacon, The vantage point from which to venture anywhere in New York, from a hotel you'll want to come home to.</TD></TR></TABLE></P></TD></TR><TR><TD ALIGN="right"><IMG SRC="img/couple.gif" ALT="" WIDTH="58" HEIGHT="105" HSPACE="0" VSPACE="0" BORDER="0"></A></TD><TD ALIGN="right"><TABLE BORDER=0 CELLSPACING="0" CELLPADDING="0">	<TR>		<TD ALIGN="right"><A HREF="http://www.res.beaconhotel.com" onMouseOver = "imgOn('img1')"  onMouseOut = "imgOff('img1')" TARGET="new"><IMG NAME="img1" SRC="img/but/res.gif" ALT="Reservations" WIDTH="109" HEIGHT="13" HSPACE="0" VSPACE="5" BORDER="0"></A><BR><A HREF="rooms.html" onMouseOver = "imgOn('img3')"  onMouseOut = "imgOff('img3')" TARGET="_parent"><IMG NAME="img3" SRC="img/but/rooms.gif" ALT="Rooms" WIDTH="54" HEIGHT="13" HSPACE="0" VSPACE="5" BORDER="0"></A><BR><A HREF="rooms.html#rates" onMouseOver = "imgOn('img4')"  onMouseOut = "imgOff('img4')" TARG